Maintainer: PantheonChain Foundation <contact@pantheonchain.org>
Description: PantheonChain — three-layer hybrid blockchain
 PantheonChain is a production-grade multi-layer blockchain consisting of:
  - TALANTON (L1): SHA-256d Proof-of-Work settlement layer (21M TALN cap)
  - DRACHMA  (L2): PoS/BFT payment and validator layer (41M DRM cap)
  - OBOLOS   (L3): EVM-compatible smart-contract execution layer (61M OBL cap)
 .
 Features:
  - Schnorr signatures (BIP-340) across all layers
  - Cross-layer commitment anchoring (OBOLOS → DRACHMA → TALANTON)
  - Governance: 1A1V voting, veto, parameter changes, emergency actions
  - Full node daemon, CLI, relayer daemons, and hardware wallet support
 .
 Binaries installed: pantheon-l1-talanton-node, pantheon-l2-drachma-node,
  pantheon-l3-obolos-node, pantheon-cli, pantheon-relayer-l2, pantheon-relayer-l3
Homepage: https://pantheonchain.org
